<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">documentation</ENAMEX> and interviews obtained from our site visits, we
compared practices across <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">organizations</ENAMEX> to identify innovative
practices used by individual <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">organizations</ENAMEX> as well as common
